'''2-Chlorophenol''' or '''''ortho''-chlorophenol''' is a noxious-smelling, slightly acidic liquid (its [[pKa]] is 8.83).  It is a known [[pollutant]] of [[aquifer]]s, a precursor of [[dye]]s, and a [[disinfectant]] agent.

